    "Question": {
      "content": "Three capacitors of capacitances 0.4µF, 0.1µF and 0.5µF are in parallel and charged to a potential difference of 50V, determine the total charge acquired",
      "type": "OBJ",
      "options": [
        "45µC",
        "4.5µC",
        "50µC",
        "3.5µC"
      ]
    },
    "Answer": {
      "type": "string",
      "content": "50µC"
    },
    "Explanation": {
      "type": "string",
      "content": "<p><b>Step 1:</b> Total capacitance in parallel:</p> \\[ C_{total} = 0.4µF + 0.1µF + 0.5µF = 1.0µF \\] <p><b>Step 2:</b> Calculate total charge:</p> \\[ Q = C_{total} \\times V = 1.0µF \\times 50V = 50µC \\]"
    },
