    "Question": {
      "content": "Three lamps each of 240Ω are connected in parallel across a 240V supply. Compute the power dissipated in the circuit.",
      "type": "OBJ",
      "options": [
        "24W",
        "720W",
        "19200W",
        "2160W"
      ]
    },
    "Answer": {
      "type": "string",
      "content": "720W"
    },
    "Explanation": {
      "type": "string",
      "content": "Power per lamp = V²/R = (240V)²/240Ω = 240W. Total power for 3 lamps in parallel: 3 × 240W = 720W."
    },
